original: A helmet crafted from the carefully cleaned and pruned exoskeletons of fire ants.  Covers the entire head. fire-resistant and very durable.
translation: 一种由经过仔细清理和修剪的火蚁外骨骼制成的头盔。覆盖整个头部。耐火，非常耐用。

original: A huge, crimson beast covered in visible scarring from what you can only guess was 'research'.  Being near it, you can feel intense heat emanating from it.
translation: 一头巨大的深红色野兽身上布满了你只能猜测是“研究”留下的可见疤痕。靠近它，你能感觉到它散发出强烈的热量。

original: A human body with crimson flesh, occasionally a flicker of flame can be seen.
translation: 一个人身上有着深红色的肉，偶尔可以看到一闪一闪的火焰。

original: A hunched human body with its eyes pushed up into its forehead and drooping cheeks, most of its face is occupied by a puckered mouth.  Its stomach is swollen and nearly translucent, with a sickly colorless tint.
translation: 一个驼背的人体，眼睛向上伸入前额，脸颊下垂，脸的大部分被皱起的嘴占据。它的胃肿胀，几乎半透明，有一种病态的无色色调。

original: A insectoid robot the size of a small dog, designed for extreme breaching. Primed with a small beeping sound, it can skate across the ground with great speed.
translation: 一种类似于小狗大小的昆虫机器人，设计用于极限突破。一个小哔哔声启动，它可以滑过地面以极大的速度。

original: A insectoid robot the size of a small dog, designed for firey entries. Primed with a small beeping sound, it can skate across the ground with great speed.
translation: 一种类似昆虫的机器人，有小狗那么大，专为有火的进入而设计。一个小哔哔声启动，它可以滑过地面以极大的速度。

original: A lump of exoskeleton that has a firey-orange sheen to it.  It is fire-resistant, warm to the touch, and remarkably sturdy.
translation: 一块有火橙色光泽的外骨骼。它是防火，温暖的触摸，并显着坚固。

original: A massive firey-orange ant that towers over the worker ants with a giant head crest.  Along with its huge mandibles, a highly violatie ooze seeps from the end of its bloated abdomen.
translation: 一种巨大的火橙色蚂蚁，顶在工蚁的头顶上，有一个巨大的头冠。随着它巨大的下颚，一种高度紫色的软泥从它臃肿的腹部渗出。

original: A monster pack that adds several fire type monsters to the game.
translation: 在游戏中加入几个火类怪物的怪物群。

original: A monstrous firey-orange ant with a slighty, glowing abdomen, that ends with a small stinger at the tip.
translation: 一种凶猛的橙色火蚁，腹部细长发光，末端有一个小毒刺。

original: A pair of arm guards crafted from the carefully cleaned and pruned exoskeletons of fire ants. Fire-resistant and very durable.
translation: 一对护臂，由经过仔细清理和修剪的火蚁外骨骼制成。耐火，非常耐用。

original: A sickly-looking dead one.  Its skin looks especially thin, with a peculiar, colorless fluid flowing through the clearly visible veins.
translation: 一个病态的死人。它的皮肤看起来特别薄，有一种特殊的无色液体流过清晰可见的静脉。

original: A squirming light-yellow grub that seems to be drippling a tanish jellified-liquid from both ends of its body.
translation: 一种蠕动的浅黄色蛴螬，似乎从身体两端滴下棕褐色的胶状液体。

original: AI tag for when monsters are hit by player.  This is a bug if you have it.
translation: 当怪物被玩家击中时的AI标签。这是一个错误，如果你有它。

original: An enormous firey-orange ant with an elongated, pulsating abdomen.  Its orifice seems developed only for egg-laying rather than spraying flammable napalm like the rest of the colony, but it doesn't seem affected by fire either.
translation: 一种巨大的火橙色蚂蚁，腹部细长、跳动。它的孔口似乎只为产卵而开发，而不是像其他殖民地一样喷洒易燃的凝固汽油弹，但它似乎也不受火灾的影响。

original: Boots crafted from carefully cleaned and pruned exoskeletons of fire ants. Fire-resistant and very durable.
translation: 由经过仔细清理和修剪的火蚁外骨骼制成的靴子。耐火，非常耐用。

original: Durable fire chitin plating made for a vehicle.
translation: 耐用的消防甲壳素电镀车辆。

original: Fake gun that fires napalm globs.
translation: 发射凝固汽油弹的假枪。
发射凝固汽油弹的假枪。

original: Fire ant manibles click with a spark, launching a glob of firey spit!
translation: 火蚁手用火星发出咔哒声，发射出一个火球！

original: Fire ant manibles click with a spark, launching firey spit!
translation: 火蚁手用火花发出咔哒声，发出火吐！

original: Gauntlets crafted from the carefully cleaned and pruned exoskeletons of fire ants. Fire-resistant and very durable.
translation: 用经过仔细清理和修剪的火蚁外骨骼制成的手套。耐火，非常耐用。

original: Incendiary zombie spits a wad of fire!
Incendiary zombie vomits up a glob of flamming spit!
translation: 燃烧的丧尸吐出一团燃烧的唾沫！

original: Leg and body armor crafted from the carefully cleaned and pruned exoskeletons of fire ants. Fire-resistant and very durable.
translation: 由经过仔细清理和修剪的火蚁外骨骼制成的腿甲和防弹衣。耐火，非常耐用。

original: Red stinger taken from an fire ant thats been reinforced with fire chintin into a knife. Left over venom residue might have some effect if a vital is hit.
translation: 从一只火蚁身上取下的红色毒刺，被火烧成一把刀。残留的毒液可能会有一些影响，如果一个重要的是击中。

original: Red stinger taken from an fire ant thats been strapped to a stick giving increased reach at cost of durability. Left over venom residue might have some effect if a vital is hit.
translation: 从一只火蚁身上取下的红色毒刺，它被绑在一根棍子上，以耐久性为代价增加了触角。残留的毒液可能会有一些影响，如果一个重要的是击中。

original: Red stinger taken from an fire ant. Left over venom residue might have some effect if a vital is hit. Useful weapon in a pinch, but handling by itself is difficult
translation: 从火蚁身上取下的红色毒刺。残留的毒液可能会有一些影响，如果一个重要的是击中。在紧急情况下是有用的武器，但单独处理是困难的

original: Spitter vomits out a glob of firey spit!
translation: 吐唾沫的人吐出一团火状的唾沫！

original: Tank discharges a massive napalm bomb!
translation: 坦克发射了一枚巨大的凝固汽油弹！

original: The %1$s tries to set <npcname> on fire, but fails to.
The %1$s tries to set you on fire, but fails to.
The %1$s tries to slam into <npcname>, but fails to.
The %1$s tries to slam into you, but stumbles aside.
translation: %1$s试图撞上你，但却摔倒在一边。

original: The %1$s tries to sting <npcname>, but fails to penetrate their armor!
translation: %1$s试图刺<npcname>，但未能穿透他们的装甲！

original: The %1$s tries to sting you, but fails to penetrate your armor!
translation: %1$s试图刺你，但未能穿透你的盔甲！

original: The Northrop Exterminator F-4 was a production series of flamethrower exterminator robots. Commissioned & designed for use of controlled burns, and extreme pest control, it rolls on a set of hydraulic treads and is armed with an intimidating flamethrower.
translation: 诺斯罗普歼灭机F-4是一个生产系列的喷火机歼灭机器人。经过调试和设计，可用于控制烧伤和极端害虫控制，它在一套液压踏板上滚动，并配备有一个令人生畏的喷火器。

original: The Northrop Exterminator FT-X was a prototype series of flamethrower exterminator tanks. Clearly engineered by a someone who found a nest of unspeakable critters that drove that person to convert the F-4's into overkill Flamethrower tanks also armed with vulcan napalm bomb launchers.
translation: 诺斯罗普灭火器FT-X是一个原型系列的火焰喷射灭火器坦克。显然是有人设计的，他发现了一窝难以形容的小动物，驱使他把F-4改装成了杀伤力超强的喷火坦克，还装备了火神凝固汽油弹发射器。

original: This body has swollen to immense proportions, but still manages to hold itself together with semi-congealed colorless liquid all over its bloated body.  It clumsily moves around, but somehow attacks with a large reserve of highly flammable liquid.
translation: 这个身体已经膨胀到巨大的比例，但仍然设法保持自己与半凝固无色液体在其肿胀的身体。它笨手笨脚地四处移动，但不知何故，它会带着大量的易燃液体攻击。

original: This is an inactive explosive skitterbot. It resembles a dog size insect packed with explosives. Using this item involves placing it on the ground and turning it on.  If reprogrammed and rewired successfully the robot will race towards enemies and explode.
translation: 这是一个不活跃的爆炸性跳跃机器人。它像一只狗大小的昆虫，里面装满了炸药。使用这个项目涉及到把它放在地上，并把它打开。如果重新编程和重新布线成功，机器人将向敌人飞奔并爆炸。

original: This is an inactive exterminator robot. It resembles a security bot only armed with a flamethrower. Using this item involves placing it on the ground and turning it on.  If reprogrammed and rewired successfully the robot will race towards enemies and torch them alive.
translation: 这是一个不活跃的灭虫机器人。它就像一个只有喷火器的安全机器人。使用这个项目涉及到把它放在地上，并把它打开。如果重新编程和重新布线成功，机器人将向敌人飞奔，并将他们活活烧死。

original: This is an inactive exterminator tank. It resembles a large tank only armed with a flamethrower & napalm bomb launchers. Using this item involves placing it on the ground and turning it on.  If reprogrammed and rewired successfully the tank will race towards enemies and torch them alive.
translation: 这是一个无效的灭虫罐。它就像一个只配备了火焰喷射器和凝固汽油弹发射器的大型坦克。使用这个项目涉及到把它放在地上，并把它打开。如果重新编程和重新布线成功，坦克将冲向敌人，并将他们活活烧死。

original: This is an inactive incendiary skitterbot. It resembles a dog size insect packed with incendiary explosives. Using this item involves placing it on the ground and turning it on.  If reprogrammed and rewired successfully the robot will race towards enemies and explode.
translation: 这是一个不活跃的燃烧跳跃机器人。它就像一只狗大小的昆虫，里面装满了燃烧炸药。使用这个项目涉及到把它放在地上，并把它打开。如果重新编程和重新布线成功，机器人将向敌人飞奔并爆炸。

original: This once-human is visible only as a glowing crimson silhouette that you have to squint to see, cloaked in a  field of flames that flicker intensely. It walks slowly and deliberately, the raging inferno around it dances wildly.
translation: 这个曾经的人类只有当你眯着眼睛才能看到的红彤彤的轮廓，隐藏在一片强烈闪烁的火焰中。它慢条斯理地走着，周围狂怒的地狱狂舞着。
易变的丧尸喷出火焰般的唾沫！

original: With its ember skin swollen to near rupture with methane gas, this cyst covered zombie looks like it could violently burst under the slightest of disturbances, and fire would probably be a very bad idea.
translation: 由于灰烬的皮肤被甲烷气体膨胀到几乎破裂，这个被囊肿覆盖的丧尸看起来像是在轻微的干扰下就可以猛烈地爆裂，着火可能是一个非常糟糕的主意。
非活动爆炸物跳跃机器人
不活跃的燃烧跳跃机器人

original: pair of fire chitin arm guards
pairs of fire chitin arm guards
